  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Death in the Night is a game in which you have to collect the souls of cats and overcome deadly traps.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gloomy atmosphere<br></li><li>Deadly traps<br></li><li>Saws, a lot of saws<br></li><li>Cats (souls of cats)<br></li><li>Levers, teleports, doors<br></li><li>Complete the levels and get achievements.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >History:</h2>The main character is death, collecting the souls of animals.<br>What happened in this world? There is no answer to this question, but you can run jump and squat in a deadly puzzle platformer game.",
